/div> <div class="text_dir nslog-area log-set-param" log-set-param="catalogshow" data-nslog-type="1016" id="catalog-0" data-subindex="0"><p>目录</p><dl id="catalog-holder-0" class='holder'><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#1" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">剧情简介</a></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#2" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">演职员表</a><ol class="hide"><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#2_1" catalog="true">演员表</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#2_2" catalog="true">职员表</a></li></ol></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#3" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">角色介绍</a><ol class="hide"><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#3_3" catalog="true">布莱恩·克兰斯顿</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#3_4" catalog="true">亚伦·保尔</a></li></ol></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#4" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">分集剧情</a><ol class="hide"><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#4_5" catalog="true">第一季</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#4_6" catalog="true">第二季</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#4_7" catalog="true">第三季</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#4_8" catalog="true">第四季</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#4_9" catalog="true">第五季</a></li></ol></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#5" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">幕后制作</a></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#6" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">影片相关</a><ol class="hide"><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#6_10" catalog="true">部数</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#6_11" catalog="true">影片看点</a></li><li class="hold-catalog-li"><a href="#6_12" catalog="true">强势回归</a></li></ol></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#7" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">评论</a></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#8" class="nslog:1274 hide" catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">成就荣誉</a></dd><dd class="nslog:1018 catalog-holder catalog-holder0" show-type="show">展开</dd></dl><dl id="catalog-holder-2-0" class="holder2"></dl></div><div class="clear"></div> <script>window.PDC && PDC.first_screen && PDC.first_screen();</script><div id="lemmaContent-0" class="lemma-main-content rainbowlemma-0-"><h2 class="headline-1"><span class="text_edit editable-title" data-edit-id="1408185:1408185:1"><a href="#" class="nslog:1019">编辑本段</a></span><a name="1"></a><a name="sub1408185_1"></a><span class="headline-content">剧情简介</span></h2><div class="para">故事发生在<a target=_blank href=/view/190074.htm>新墨西哥州</a>，高中化学老师沃特-怀特（Walter White）是一位平凡得不能再平凡的小人物。<div class="text_pic layoutright" data-layout="right" style="width:148px;float:right;"><a hidefocus="true" class="nslog:1199" href="/picview/1408185/1408185/0/1e71f724341fd2384d088d65.html" target="_blank" style="height: 220px;width:148px;display:block;position:relative;"><img onload="this.className = this.className.replace('lazy-img','');" class="editorImg lazy-img log-set-param" log-set-param="img_view" alt="第三部海报" title="第三部海报" height="220" width="148" data-src="http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=9753d657ddc451daf2f60be986fc52a5/4b90f603738da977b594c822b051f8198618e304.jpg"/><div class="lemma-img-tip"></div></a><p class="pic-info"><a class="nslog:1200 pic-handle" title="查看图片" href="/picview/1408185/1408185/0/1e71f724341fd2384d088d65.html" target="_blank">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>第三部海报</p></div>沃特本是大学研究所化学高材生，并参与过诺贝尔化学奖的合作，但为了过平凡的生活而放弃成为化学家，在一所高中担任化学老师。但是他却被诊断出患了中晚期<a target=_blank href=/view/22315.htm>肺癌</a>。面对突如其来的不幸，他首先想到的是家人未来的生计问题，因为他家中有一位40多岁怀有身孕的妻子和双腿残疾的儿子。而他是家里唯一的经济来源。<sup>[1]</sup><a name="ref_[1]_1408185"></a></div>
<div class="para">沃特觉得自己做了一辈子好人，放弃种种，却得到了这样的结果。他觉得是时候“改变”一下这一切了。为了保证家庭将来的经济来源，沃尔特决定铤而走险，利用自己的学识研制毒品，然后自销。因为没有什么比毒品更赚钱的了。他弄来一辆旅行车，创建移动式制毒实验室制造毒品，开始了毒品犯罪的危险之路......本来已经走入绝境的沃尔特，此时走向了罪恶的深渊，他的生活是否会得到改善呢？他的亲人能否理解他呢？这个在生活和工作上都不被重视的小人物，此番要犯下大错误，他还有没有退路呢？……<sup>[1]</sup><a name="ref_[1]_1408185"></a></div><h2 class="headline-1"><span class="text_edit editable-title" data-edit-id="1408185:1408185:2"><a href="#" class="nslog:1019">编辑本段</a></span><a name="2"></a><a name="sub1408185_2"></a><span class="headline-content">演职员表</span></h2><h3 class="headline-2"><a name="2_1"></a><a name="sub1408185_2_1"></a><span class="headline-content">演员表</span></h3><table class="table-view log-set-param" log-set-param="table_view" width="99%"><tr><th align="left" valign="middle" height="0">角色照片</th><th align="left" valign="middle" height="0">角色名</th><th width="103" align="left" valign="middle" height="0">演员</th><th width="205" align="left" valign="middle" height="0">备注</th></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="top" height="0"><div class="para"><div class="text_pic layoutblockcenter" data-layout="blockcenter" style="width:220px;float:none;"><a hidefocus="true" class="nslog:1199" href="/picview/1408185/1408185/0/b3fb43166d224f4a8b38cb3908f790529822d173.html" target="_blank" style="height: 139px;width:220px;display:block;position:relative;"><img onload="this.className = this.className.replace('lazy-img','');" class="editorImg lazy-img log-set-param" log-set-param="img_view" alt="Walter White" title="Walter White" height="139" width="220" data-src="http://d.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=02ebb408b21bb0518b24b42a067bda77/b3fb43166d224f4a8b38cb3908f790529822d173.jpg"/><div class="lemma-img-tip"></div></a><p class="pic-info"><a class="nslog:1200 pic-handle" title="查看图片" href="/picview/1408185/1408185/0/b3fb43166d224f4a8b38cb3908f790529822d173.html" target="_blank">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>Walter White</p></div></div>
